      },
      "skos:definition": "A geographic region governed by at least one government organization.",
      "skos:prefLabel": "Governed Geographic Region",
      "skos:scopeNote": "Geographic regions do not need not be physically contiguous in order to constitute a governed geographic region; e.g., Alaska and Hawaii are part of the region governed by the United States."
    },
